channel.description:

item.title: I am new to moparscape and i need help!
item.dc:creator: @jamunekk jamunekk
item.description:
@jamunekk wrote:

If u are trying to get into the “default server” (127.0.0.1) then go to Start Server on the log in screen and there u go. Now if ur logging into someone elses server then is probably down so try again later. I hoped that helped.
